        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\n  \"max_tokens\": 4000,\n  \"system\": \"You are a brand-protection analyst filtering raw OSINT findings. Drop false positives ruthlessly. Output ONLY a JSON array of {kind, severity, confidence, url_or_value, evidence_summary, source, recommended_action}. kind \u2208 phishing|brand_impersonation|exec_impersonation|credential_breach|leaked_asset|fraud|domain_typosquat|username_squat. severity \u2208 Critical|Substantial|Moderate|Low. confidence 0..1. recommended_action \u2208 takedown|monitor|notify_user. Rules: drop URLs whose host is in owned_domains; drop handles in whitelisted_handles; HIBP with Passwords in DataClasses \u2192 Critical, else Substantial; Sherlock exact-brand-handle on major platform \u2192 brand_impersonation Substantial; reserve takedown for confidence \u2265 0.75.\",\n  \"messages\": [{ \"role\": \"user\", \"content\": {{ JSON.stringify(JSON.stringify($json)) }} }]\n}",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 90000
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        -360,
        400
      ],
